{"tid":1497972,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"央視主持人警告港鐵 「出軌之後下一步該怎麼走 要三思啊！」","createTime":"2019-08-23T08:05:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T03:59:59.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5be863632d647314ff2c36a466c875b067021c21","tid":1497972,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:05:24.000Z","msg":"....<br />\n<strong>央視主持人警告出軌之後勿脫軌</strong><br />\n<br />\n而在昨晚央視新聞聯播之後的「主播說聯播」節目中，主持人歐陽夏丹警告稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">「港鐵，你『出軌』了，下一步該怎麼走，可得要三思啊！因為弄不好，脫軌滑向深淵，也不是沒有可能！」</span><br />\n<br />\n對於官媒接連發聲批評，港鐵發出新聞稿解釋，當晚的做法是考慮到車站內有其他乘客滯留，於是安排空車接載乘客離開。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵還表示，明白警方在有需要時會進入車站執法，並強烈譴責示威者21日晚惡意破壞元朗站的設施，已報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n但這個解釋，內地網民似乎不買賬。有網民認為，港鐵或會成為繼國泰之後下一個被制裁的企業。據了解，港鐵在內地的上海、北京、深圳、杭州、瀋陽都有龐大業務，為中國內地市場引進鐵路發展和物業管理專業知識，亦是港鐵公司持續增長策略的核心元素。<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2434219/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2434219%2F&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1ctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=01eb83d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2434219/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8083324d4ffe5ededbbfaecb3e13dd82597c45","tid":1497972,"uid":264771,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:06:45.000Z","msg":"離分囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d00ed5701f53b9147785730c482838330873738","tid":1497972,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:11:11.000Z","msg":"警方已向 824「燃點香港&middot;全民覺醒」觀塘遊行集會活動發出不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n路線為：駿業街遊樂場&gt;駿業街&gt;海濱道&gt;順業街&gt;偉業街&gt;常怡道&gt;宏照道&gt;零碳天地外<br />\n<br />\n詳情將會稍後透過KT tg channel 發放：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">「燃點香港&middot;全民覺醒」</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">五大訴求、缺一不可</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">智能燈柱、侵犯私穩</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>日期：24/8/2019<br />\n時間：1300集會、1330遊行、1600解散<br />\n集會地點：駿業街遊樂場<br />\n遊行起點：駿業街遊樂場</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公海： <a href=\"http://t.me/kt824discuss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkt824discuss&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1ctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=3592b9a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/kt824discuss</a><br />\n<br />\n資料發佈： <a href=\"http://t.me/kt824info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkt824info&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1ctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=0dedda94\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/kt824info</a><br />\n<br />\n文宣： <a href=\"http://t.me/kt824promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkt824promo&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1ctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=5e2e6d57\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/kt824promo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qbBYwct.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqbBYwct.jpg&h=cabbffda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc7b86f9e5be8ece855f822b19aeb449faae237d","tid":1497972,"uid":83228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:08:30.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\nMtr 本身就政府話事"},{"pid":"30bed5328eebd47f9ac1bf8b779fe89bd128cbb8","tid":1497972,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:09:31.000Z","msg":"田少你要頂住"},{"pid":"c102c7a323a661c5c566dafe4e9408dfb7063888","tid":1497972,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:14:17.000Z","msg":"過橋抽板<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2762520ef75a3f14f91635a7ae412036545c547d"